"{\n  \"text\": \"Hey everybody, Scotty here. I'm the owner of Scotty's Fermented Foods. I wanted to talk to you about my kimchi today. I have a vegan, a traditional, and a white kimchi. The traditional has fish sauce. It's Napa Cabbage, Daikon radishes, carrots, onions, garlic, ginger, and green onions all done up in a hot pepper paste. Kochuru. We do a vegan, which is all the same ingredients, minus the fish sauce for those of you who don't want fish sauce or don't like fish sauce. And then I also do a white kimchi. This is all the vegetables minus the fish sauce minus the hot pepper paste. This is for people who don't like the spice. You can get all my products at Scotty'sFoods.com. I have a special. If you order any four products, you get free shipping. I know I'm just some crazy white dude trying to sell Korean food, but I make good kimchi. I need you to trust me on this one. Try it and you won't regret it. Thanks a lot, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, Scotty here.\",\n      \"start\": 0.64,\n      \"end\": 2.16,\n      \"duration\": 1.52,\n      \"confidence\": 0.992,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 0.64,\n          \"end\": 0.88,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.998\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 0.88,\n          \"end\": 0.96,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 1.04,\n          \"end\": 1.12,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 1.12,\n          \"end\": 1.2,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ody\",\n          \"start\": 1.2,\n          \"end\": 1.36,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n   